Biography

Jason Nadboy is an undergraduate at Brown University concentrating in Computer Science. His coursework includes Mathematics, Physics, Jewish Studies and Computer Science. He was a teaching assistant (TA) his junior year for a class covering algorithms and data structures. He interned as a software engineer during summer 2016 and a history intern during summer 2015.
